metadata.name: GALAXSEA
metadata.description:
where the sea meets the sky  
where the sea meets the sands  
shore below just turns as the same space as galaxy above

and the body... this body is made of sky and stars, rivers and oceans, earth and gold, masquerading as muscle and bone. every cell is an organ of sense, infused with majesty

we are the GALAXSEA

by @KyleVollaers X @soulthesea
